ass=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/dbfced5189f77ff95eb112c16ed8f0bc.webp?t=1772800792\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help cities grow by satisfying their needs for goods, food and luxury goods. Big cities provide more passengers which can be transported to nearby cities profitably. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/462486ccf675170d057284d655c238a9.poster.avif?t=1772800792\" width=500 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/462486ccf675170d057284d655c238a9.webm?t=1772800792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/462486ccf675170d057284d655c238a9.mp4?t=1772800792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/09f554b10e11b442506316363dd8eefd.webp?t=1772800792\" width=500 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transport 40 different goods between 39 different industries and numerous cities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep your station stock low to get a production bonus from industry buildings. Deliver machinery and tools to industry buildings to get a production boost for a short period of time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/659920/extras/043b390b50a8134c8fd50a1411505034.poster.avif?t=1772800792\" width=500 height=100 ><source src=\"https://s